            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-607163425" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-607163425" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="607163425">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52296901/">平卢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">【图书馆】自幼被灌输马教史观，实在厌烦。历史的解释本该多样。不知道是翻译的原因还是怎么，有错字和史实错误，窦太后是景帝之妃？真心不喜社科的书。PS：大量引用廿二史札记= =</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1031228965">
